Author: imjustlurkinganyway
Text: This makes a lot of sense to me. A lot. I had been on Effexor, and had the same kind of weight gain. I felt weird because it's like I wanted to be happy that I was having healthier thoughts (I don't know if you'd call in that, but lack of a better term) but at the same time I didn't want to let go of it, even though it was terrifying it was also safe to me. I have been off it for a while now and I have spiraled back down. For what it's worth, I know it's hard to "miss" your ED. PM me if you ever want to talk about it. Stay strong. <3
